Geometry Dash World - Chrome Extension
Get ready to jump and dash in Geometry Dash World, the thrilling Chrome Extension that brings the iconic rhythm-based platformer to your browser!

In this exciting game, you'll navigate through a series of challenging levels filled with obstacles, spikes, and dynamic soundtracks. With simple one-touch controls, you'll need to time your jumps perfectly to conquer each level and avoid crashing. The vibrant graphics and engaging animations create a captivating experience that keeps you coming back for more.

Geometry Dash World features a variety of new levels and unique challenges, ensuring that both newcomers and seasoned players will find plenty of excitement. Customize your character with unlockable icons and colors as you progress through the game.

Perfect for players of all ages, Geometry Dash World combines skill, timing, and rhythm for an addictive gaming experience.

Download Geometry Dash World and start your rhythmic adventure today!

Avoid the spikes and other deadly obstacles as you help your cube through to the end of the level. There are three different characters, one where you can flap through the air. Try to complete all three levels in as few attempts as possible in this Geometry Dash genre game.
